data.description: Presenting an exceptional residence in the Oak Shores development on Lake Nacimiento. This beautifully maintained 2007 craftsman-style residence offers an idyllic retreat for full-time or part-time living. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek stainless appliances, a beautiful tile backsplash, ample cabinets, a built-in wine refrigerator, and a breakfast bar that complements the generous counter space. The home boasts family rooms on each level, with vaulted ceilings upstairs that create an open and airy ambiance. The master bedroom is truly grand, boasting a walk-in closet, a luxurious bathroom with dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a step-in shower that offers a captivating peek-a-boo view of the lake. The convenience of an upstairs laundry room with a wash sink, a whole house fan, comfortable-sized bedrooms, and ceiling fans throughout ensure a truly comfortable living experience. Explore the impressive 3-car garage, complete with a boat-depth stall to store your lake toys. With ample driveway parking and an additional spot parallel to the driveway dedicated to this home, you'll never have to worry about parking. The yard is an inviting oasis, perfect for outdoor entertaining and activities. You'll enjoy the patio area, which is covered by a spacious upper deck. Being in a gated community provides added security and privacy, ensuring a peaceful and tranquil environment. Oak Shores offers an abundance of amenities, including ~ a new pickleball court, solar heated swimming pool + kids pool, marina, clubhouse, gated entry and MORE! Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity – call now to schedule your viewing.
